---
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Button from "@/components/fundations/elements/Button.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-8 lg:pb-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 items-start gap-8 mt-2">
      <div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <Text
            tag="p"
            variant="textSM"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
            class="text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-300 font-medium tracking-widest uppercase"
          >
            翰霖法律事務所
          </Text>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden mt-4">
          <Text
            tag="h1"
            variant="displayLG"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1500"
            class="dark:text-white text-base-900 text-balance"
          >
            專業、誠信
            <br />
            守護您的每一份權益
          </Text>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <Text
            tag="p"
            variant="textBase"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="2000"
            class="mt-4 text-base-500 dark:text-base-300 lg:text-balance"
          >
            我們以豐富的法律實務經驗與堅定的專業信念，為每一位當事人提供全方位的法律服務。從諮詢到執行，翰霖始終與您同在。
          </Text>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8">
          <Button
            isLink
            size="base"
            variant="default"
            href="/contact"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="2000"
          >
            立即諮詢
          </Button>
          <Button
            isLink
            size="base"
            variant="muted"
            href="/practice-areas"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="2200"
          >
            專業領域
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex lg:ml-auto lg:justify-end"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="2000"
      >
        <div class="p-8 bg-base-50 dark:bg-base-900 w-full max-w-md">
          <Text
            tag="h3"
            variant="textLG"
            class="dark:text-white text-base-900 font-medium"
          >
            免費初步諮詢
          </Text>
          <Text
            tag="p"
            variant="textSM"
            class="text-base-500 dark:text-base-400 mt-2"
          >
            我們提供免費的初步法律諮詢，讓您了解案件狀況與可行方案。
          </Text>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="size-4 text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-300 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
              </svg>
              <Text tag="span" variant="textSM" class="text-base-700 dark:text-base-300">
                02-2585-2626
              </Text>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="size-4 text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-300 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 0115 0z" />
              </svg>
              <Text tag="span" variant="textSM" class="text-base-700 dark:text-base-300">
                台北市中正區重慶南路一段99號11樓之9
              </Text>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
</section>
